name: Panoramas of Paris
description:
This is a beautifully made, 22 page, hand crafted booklet that is presented in a hand-stitched denim sleeve. There are 12 professionally printed images and 10 images that were printed onto the page using a method called cyanatype [3 of which are stained].

	Contained features:
- Leather bound, stitched spine
- 12 printed images
- 10 cyanatype images [3 stained]
- Denim sleeve
